    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231550/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.poster.avif?t=1695228259\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231550/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.webm?t=1695228259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231550/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.mp4?t=1695228259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在迷人的图形和沉浸式音轨的陪衬下，&quot;The Traveler's Path&quot; 是一款富有挑战性和趣味性的游戏，将测试您的解谜技能。帮助英雄抵达目的地并开辟新的道路。每个关卡都呈现出独特的路径和障碍组合，玩家必须使用自己的创造力和技巧找到完美的解决方案。<br><br>您准备好踏上这场探索与冒险之旅了吗？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231550/extras/f0a57da26e1419abafc053db5050396d.poster.avif?t=1695228259\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231550/extras/f0a57da26e1419abafc053db5050396d.webm?t=1695228259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231550/extras/f0a57da26e1419abafc053db5050396d.mp4?t=1695228259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>特点</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>超过50个具有不同主题和机制的富有挑战性的关卡。<br></li><li>直观且反应灵敏的控制，保证流畅的游戏体验。<br></li><li>每个谜题都有多种解决方案，鼓励创造性思考。<br></li><li>难度逐渐增加，允许玩家以自己的步伐进展。<br></li><li>完成挑战和达成里程碑可解锁成就和奖励。<br></li><li>适合所有年龄段的人，为每个人提供有趣且富有挑战性的谜题。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231550/extras/2e8526f9aecb33b4eb3d833036e4d90f.poster.avif?t=1695228259\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231550/extras/2e8526f9aecb33b4eb3d833036e4d90f.webm?t=1695228259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231550/extras/2e8526f9aecb33b4eb3d833036e4d90f.mp4?t=1695228259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>在谜题的世界中征服旅行者的道路！</strong>",
